        "question_text": "Topic Used: Finding the nth term of an AP using $a_n = a_1 + (n-1)d$ where $a_1$ and $d$ are given.\n\nIn an arithmetic progression, the first term ($a_1$) is 8 and the common difference ($d$) is 6. What is the value of the $11^{th}$ term ($a_{11}$)?",
